<div class="email-header">
  <h1>Welcome to Listopia!</h1>
</div>

<div class="email-body">
  <p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>
  <p>Thanks for signing up for Listopia! To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="<%= @verification_url %>" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
  </div>
  <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f7f4ee; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #d9d2c1; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">
    <%= @verification_url %>
  </p>
  <p>Once verified, you'll be able to:</p>
  <ul style="color: #13243a; line-height: 1.8;">
    <li>Create and organize your lists</li>
    <li>Collaborate with others in real-time</li>
    <li>Access your lists from anywhere</li>
    <li>And much more!</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666666; margin-bottom: 8px;">If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666666;">Welcome aboard!<br><strong>The Listopia Team</strong></p>
</div>